title: Led Zeppelin - Celebration Day AVCHD BD5 720p DTS NTSC rECOn
description:
Led Zeppelin - Celebration Day AVCHD BD5 720p DTS NTSC rECOn

Of course, Led Zeppelin needs no introduction.  This video was rECOnstructed from the blue ray disk release in 2012.  While the performance and sound quality are both top notch, unfortunately the video was presented in PAL format.  This creates a problem for most of us located in north america because most of our players do not work with PAL material.  So the rECOn team re-encoded the video, converting the frame rate to 23.976, resized the picture to 1280x720 to preserve the video at a lower bitrate, and deinterlaced the video to progressive.  The result is quite playable for the data rate.

For audio, we used standard DTS (core) 5.1 surround sound audio.

The data fits nicely on a single sided DVD disk.  Simply drag the contents of the BDMV folder and make sure your burner is set to UDF v 2.5.
